54:34.920 --> 54:37.479
the reason they give me
a little serenity

54:37.480 --> 54:39.559
in the middle of the night,

54:39.560 --> 54:41.320
is their simplicity.

54:44.280 --> 54:46.759
If you don't know
who the good guys are,

54:46.760 --> 54:49.039
then look for the white hats.

