The white hats are good,
the rest are...

54:54.760 --> 54:56.760
..different degrees of bad.

54:58.040 --> 55:01.679
And I suppose I wish
the world was like that,

55:01.680 --> 55:05.880
but I realised,
when I was just a wee boy...

55:07.680 --> 55:09.200
..that it isn't...

55:11.040 --> 55:16.360
..that evil is always looking for
a more surprising place to hide.

