55:32.240 --> 55:35.080
..and maybe that you should
help him.

55:36.600 --> 55:38.680
But life isn't simple.

55:40.400 --> 55:44.360
He's not as good as you think,
and I'm not as bad as you think.

55:46.280 --> 55:47.919
Everything is in between,

55:47.920 --> 55:52.159
everything is murky
in this world, Erin,

55:52.160 --> 55:54.560
and you are lost within it.

55:56.640 --> 56:00.119
So let me help you
find your way out,

56:00.120 --> 56:02.200
and we'll do the same for him.

